description: Say what you will about our planet and our people. We have our flaws as any other species would at this stage of our development. Some of us still fight over which god is 'correct' or which bit of land people should die for; some of us fight over the latest sportsball game. If the arrival of the CUBEs & the strange visitors has done anything for us, it has brought us together in ways that have profound consequences for our people. At this turning point, let us look ahead and wonder at the vista of the Processing Peaks and hope whatever is to come, CUBEs or not, we can shed these petty differences once & for all.
